  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/6f6c3afbe10c726014cbca82a1c325c6.poster.avif?t=1746077193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/6f6c3afbe10c726014cbca82a1c325c6.webm?t=1746077193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/6f6c3afbe10c726014cbca82a1c325c6.mp4?t=1746077193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Pulling No Punches is a satirical game in the 2D beat'em up style with classic arcade influences and modern visuals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/f79fe232af72582d0a52b0b31991bc38.webp?t=1746077193\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>The game follows the fictional story of a global pandemic that engulfed the world and is being ignored by fanatics who do not believe that the disease is real. It is up to the main characters, 4 common citizens adequately protected with gloves and masks, to deal with these fanatics and solve the situation with the force of their own fists.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/e9b1f5585889d3ce395ebdf7ce87dd5e.poster.avif?t=1746077193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/e9b1f5585889d3ce395ebdf7ce87dd5e.webm?t=1746077193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/e9b1f5585889d3ce395ebdf7ce87dd5e.mp4?t=1746077193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/4b4bf2f259e4fc7ad132fdb0b9522be6.webp?t=1746077193\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>● 4 Co-op Local Multiplayer!<br>● 4 Characters with unique Unlockables and Moves!<br>● Use everything at your disposal to destroy your enemies: a wide variety of punches, kicks, grabs and headbutts!<br>● Handmade art painfully animated frame by frame!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/6f6c3afbe10c726014cbca82a1c325c6.poster.avif?t=1746077193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/6f6c3afbe10c726014cbca82a1c325c6.webm?t=1746077193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/6f6c3afbe10c726014cbca82a1c325c6.mp4?t=1746077193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Pulling No Punches is a satirical game in the 2D beat'em up style with classic arcade influences and modern visuals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/f79fe232af72582d0a52b0b31991bc38.webp?t=1746077193\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>The game follows the fictional story of a global pandemic that engulfed the world and is being ignored by fanatics who do not believe that the disease is real. It is up to the main characters, 4 common citizens adequately protected with gloves and masks, to deal with these fanatics and solve the situation with the force of their own fists.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/e9b1f5585889d3ce395ebdf7ce87dd5e.poster.avif?t=1746077193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/e9b1f5585889d3ce395ebdf7ce87dd5e.webm?t=1746077193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/e9b1f5585889d3ce395ebdf7ce87dd5e.mp4?t=1746077193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425760/extras/4b4bf2f259e4fc7ad132fdb0b9522be6.webp?t=1746077193\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>● 4 Co-op Local Multiplayer!<br>● 4 Characters with unique Unlockables and Moves!<br>● Use everything at your disposal to destroy your enemies: a wide variety of punches, kicks, grabs and headbutts!<br>● Handmade art painfully animated frame by frame!",
